 industrial era.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aConsumers' preferences. 0aConsumption (Economics)xSocial aspects. 0aGlobalizationxEconomic aspects. 0aIndustrializationxHistoryx21st century. 0aIndustrializationxHistoryy21st century. 0aManufacturing industriesxTechnological innovations. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Industries / Manufacturing.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030019174540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300191745423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300191745/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles